issue.body:
### Is there an existing issue for this?

### Contact Details

Discord: jaidchen

### What should this feature add?

Comfy and Automatic1111 included new DPM++ 3M samplers/schedulers in their projects that some people reported to perform slightly better for high-steps high-details creations.

Any chance to see them in one of the next releases?

- - https://github.com/AUTOMATIC1111/stable-diffusion-webui/blob/5ef669de080814067961f28357256e8fe27544f4/CHANGELOG.md?plain=1#L9
